creator: Lavatech Limited
descriptionHtml:
Napthens Solicitors
We understand how important it is to keep in contact with our clients on a regular basis and as proactively as possible. Dealing with property can be a stressful process for clients, but we believe that by harnessing the right technology, we can relieve some of the stress and pressure, whilst also creating great working relationships with our clients.

The Napthens app allows us to communicate with you quickly and enables us to provide a smooth and transparent service. As well as providing you with messages and notifications, we will also be able to send documents to your smart device and you will also be able to return information to us through the app, saving you time.

Our app will provide you with the following features:
• Enable you to view, complete and sign forms and documents, returning them to us securely
• The ability to track the progress of your transaction using a visual tracking tool
• The ability to send messages directly to your lawyer’s inbox
• Instant updates via push notifications
• Provides convenience by having instant mobile access 24/7
• A secure and electronic file of all messages, letters and documents
• Receive relevant updates, information and newsfeeds
descriptionShort: Using the latest technology to link clients to their lawyer quickly and easily.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Identity Check flow improvements
- Switch case with badge numbers on home screen
- Minor improvements and bug fixes
